demo.asn1

Class MyOtherName

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.asn1.structures.OtherName
      • demo.asn1.MyOtherName
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iaik.asn1.ASN1Type

    public class MyOtherName
extends iaik.asn1.structures.OtherName
    A simple OtherName implementation example.

    This class is used by the OtherNameDemo; it implements an OtherName with type-id "1.3.6.1.4.1.2706.2.2.1.6.2" where the value represents an UTF8-STRING.
